---
import Page from '@layouts/Page.astro';
---

<Page
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for API Hub. We respect your privacy and do not collect personal data."
>
  <div style="max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-1); margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>
    <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-3); margin: 0 0 2rem;">
      Last updated: March 2026
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-1); margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">
      Overview
    </h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 1.5rem;">
      API Hub is a static website hosted on GitHub Pages. We are committed to protecting your privacy and
      being transparent about how this site operates.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-1); margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">
      Data We Collect
    </h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 0.5rem;">
      <strong style="color: var(--text-1);">None.</strong> API Hub does not:
    </p>
    <ul style="padding-left: 1.25rem; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.8;">
      <li>Collect personal information</li>
      <li>Use cookies for tracking</li>
      <li>Share data with third parties</li>
      <li>Require user accounts or registration</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-1); margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">
      Local Storage
    </h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 1.5rem;">
      We use browser <code style="font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.875rem;">localStorage</code>
      solely to remember your theme preference (light or dark mode). This data never leaves your browser.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-1); margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">
      External Links
    </h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 1.5rem;">
      API Hub links to external API websites and the GitHub platform. These third-party sites have their own
      privacy policies, and we have no control over their content or data practices.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-1); margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">
      Hosting
    </h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 1.5rem;">
      This site is hosted on GitHub Pages. GitHub may collect basic server logs (IP address, browser type, etc.)
      as part of their standard hosting service. Please refer to
      <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub's Privacy Statement</a>
      for details.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-1); margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">
      Contact
    </h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.7; margin: 0;">
      If you have questions about this privacy policy, please open an issue on our
      <a href="https://github.com/BEKO2210/API_directory" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub repository</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</Page>
